We're back with The Indie Hour Episode thirteen! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

Check out SPECTRE HERE: https://spectreminiatures.com/

Check out WAR ETERNAL HERE: https://www.amazon.ca/War-Eternal-Savage-Combat-Century/dp/B0CSBNNC51
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 012 - SPECTRE: Operations - ROGUE WARRIORS & WAR ETERNAL
